  <section class="features" id="features">
    <h2 class="section-title">Everything Your Family Needs</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Create a beautiful baby book or family photo album website with our
      easy-to-use app — beautifully designed and accessible from anywhere.
    </p>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon gold">&#127760;</div>
        <h3>Your Own Exclusive Domain</h3>
        <p>Every site lives at its own .com — see our demos at <a href="https://www.your-childs-name.com" target="_blank"><strong>Your-Childs-Name.com</strong></a> and <a href="https://www.your-family-photo-album.com" target="_blank"><strong>Your-Family-Photo-Album.com</strong></a>. Once a domain is yours, nobody else can have it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon sage">&#128248;</div>
        <h3>Unlimited Photos</h3>
        <p>Upload your favorite photos — first steps, family vacations, holiday gatherings, reunion portraits, and everything in between. No storage limits.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon rose">&#128118;</div>
        <h3>Digital Baby Books</h3>
        <p>Track milestones month by month, record firsts, and celebrate every stage of your child's first years with beautiful page layouts designed for the journey.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon blue">&#128247;</div>
        <h3>Family Photo Albums</h3>
        <p>Preserve your family's story across decades — reunions, holidays, adventures, traditions, and the quiet everyday moments that matter most.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon blush">&#9993;</div>
        <h3>Letters &amp; Messages</h3>
        <p>Write letters to your children, your parents, or your future selves. Invite grandparents, aunts, and uncles to contribute. The most treasured pages of any album.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon ink">&#128274;</div>
        <h3>Password Protected</h3>
        <p>Keep your family's memories private. Share the password only with the people you choose — and reveal the site whenever you're ready.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ====== HOW IT WORKS ====== -->
  <section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
    <h2 class="section-title">Up and Running in Minutes</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Get your site online in minutes — no technical skills needed.
    </p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Pick Your Plan</h3>
          <p>One plan, everything included. Start a baby book for your newborn or a family album for the whole crew.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Choose Your Domain</h3>
          <p>Pick a unique .com — your child's name, your family name, or something creative. Each domain is one-of-a-kind, so claim yours before someone else does.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Download the App</h3>
          <p>Install Legacy Odyssey on your phone and log in with your new account. You'll be ready to go in under a minute.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Fill in the Memories</h3>
          <p>Upload photos, record milestones, write letters, and add family recipes. The app walks you through every section — baby book or family album.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step fade-up">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Share &amp; Treasure</h3>
          <p>Your site is live at its own .com! Share the password with family and friends — and one day, hand it down as a gift they'll treasure forever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

